rows.label: bf08400100_0030
rows.name: So, this is what the World Tree's really like...

rows.label: bf08400100_0040
rows.name:
These... They aren't leaves...
They're glyphs?

rows.label: bf08400100_0060
rows.name:
An old Iiran warship...
Didn't think there'd be any of those left...

rows.label: bf08400100_0080
rows.name: I had no idea Acedia could make it up this high.

rows.label: bf08400100_0100
rows.name:
It appears that Acedia has modified their Divine Beast
as old Temperantia did with theirs.

rows.label: bf08400100_0120
rows.name: I did not know Acedia possessed so much force.

rows.label: bf08400100_0130
rows.name: No need to ask what they plan to do with it.

rows.label: bf08400100_0140
rows.name:
They anticipated it.
That Shin and Metsu would try to ascend.

rows.label: bf08400100_0170
rows.name:
Let's hurry!
We can't let them make it to Eden!

rows.label: bf08400100_0180
rows.name:
How do we get up there though?
The anchor's not going to reach.

rows.label: bf08400100_0190
rows.name: We just need to get a bit closer...
